Snake Game Project
================

Setup
-----

1. Install Node.js and MongoDB on your system.
2. Clone the repository and navigate to the project directory.
3. Run `npm install` to install dependencies.
4. Start the server by running `node server/app.js`.
5. Open a web browser and navigate to `http://localhost:3000`.

Usage
-----

1. Select a difficulty level from the dropdown menu.
2. Use the arrow keys to control the snake.
3. Eat food to increase your score.
4. Avoid colliding with the game board boundaries or your own body.

Note: This is a basic implementation of the Snake Game project, and you may want to add additional features or improve the game logic.